{"type": "article", "id": 9078, "title": "BMW 限量版自行车", "description": "", "date": "2015-05-01T08:38:33Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 10, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606052351368vtLcBXrTxoPaMOK.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\tBMW 为了向其旗下 M 系列汽车致敬，最近特意推出了一款叫做 “Cruise M-Bike” 的限量版自行车，自行车车身采用了与 BMW M GmbH 一样的奥斯丁黄色喷漆，车头设置了一个刻有 “BMW M Bike Limited Edition” 的浮雕银牌，搭载了电力铝合金车身，碳材质组件，单独调节手把和 Shimano 液压碟刹等配置。这款自行车目前限量 500 辆，且每一款都有独立证书。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235134DYcC9kV0y5mq8BHn.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235134wAyGEJDmpuZdPelk.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"1.335\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235135GasudKW2mEwOj5F6.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"1.335\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235135wtJo3KMVrYA7CSjv.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}